Target Vaildation:
- Make sure they are infact the owners of the subnet or domain they give you
- Tools: WHOIS, NSLOOKUP, DNSRECON


Finding Subdomains:
- Finding out the subdomains of the domain
- Tools: Google Fu, dig, Nmap, Sublist3r, Bluto, crt.sh, etc.



Fingerprinting:
- Finding out what software they are using 
- Tools: Nmap, Wappalyzer, WhatWeb, BuiltWith, Netcat
